{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, compared to other neural summarization systems, the RST p w -LoRA model is more likely to be recognized for producing the highest quality summaries and less likely to be considered as generating the poorest quality summaries.",
    "GPT-4 Evaluation Inspired by Liu et al. (2023b), we engage GPT-4 to assess our candidate models using the same guidelines as our human evaluators.",
    "To ensure experimental consistency, all experiments use the identical hyper-parameters settings detailed in Appendix D. To avoid potential biases from previous interactions, we reset the conversation history prior to each query and abstain from making any further modifications.",
    "In our initial investigation, we aim to explore the extent to which GPT-4 evaluations foot_1 generally concur with human assessments in terms of both relative ranking and average scores within the same subset of 10 samples delineated in human evaluations.",
    "We then extend the evaluation to include all samples from the test sets foot_2."
  ]
}